Class Line

  • java.lang.Object
    • das.shapes.Shape
      • das.shapes.Line

  • public class Line
extends Shape
    This class models a Line. It can detect when another line is intersecting it as well a drawing a representation of the line to a Processing PApplet

    10/9/19
    Author:
